  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nIf the device is in light mode, then the status bar becomes invisible on the home screens after the background or opening a chat.\r\nRelogin fixes the issue.\r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Send the app to the background \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/230332752-1275d923-d618-47fd-879c-f6ecdf1ae9d9.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n**or**\r\n3. Open a chat/community\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/230333430-c1baca3b-947d-447e-aae1-a9e33d32c240.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: RC 1.22\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n",
